{"id":602049,"date":[{"year":1980,"month":10,"day":1}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"七律","count":"160","ytitle":"","mtitle":"国庆述怀(七律)","ftitle":"","authors":["余立"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"余立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣逢佳节意如何?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛会方开喜事多(1)。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十载曾流忧国泪(2)，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今朝幸得爱民和。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千秋大业同筹划，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四化宏图共琢磨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地春回生气好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华夏前景实堪歌。注:(1)指全国五届人大第三次会议。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(2)“文化大革命”十年浩劫，不知有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少同志为党和国家的前途担忧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗暗地流下辛酸热泪。抚今思昔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更应珍惜今日之大好形势。"}]}